Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.92,1:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the preoccupation with heaven or hell.\NAre you really uh energized by the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.71,1:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,desire to move to heaven or is it merely\Na fear of hell? So sin and guilt then
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.76,1:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,bring up all the whole fears of hell.\NParenting skills then and bringing these
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.40,1:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,things across to the child and the\Nphysical health and heredity are
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.76,1:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,profound factors in influencing our our\Nattitudes throughout all of life. So the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.12,1:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,reason we're looking at these things is\Nbecause these are life attitudes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.28,1:10:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody sitting out here in the\Naudience right now has been profoundly
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.96,1:10:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,interested by all these things in their\Nlife.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.84,1:10:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And a self-aware person looks at all\Nthese various phenomena in their life
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.88,1:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and comes to a certain understanding\Nabout why they are the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.44,1:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everybody here know why they are\Nthe way they are?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.23,1:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody don't know why the way they are?\NYou don't know why the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.67,1:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you grow up?\NWell, you need a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.76,1:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the psychiatrist comes in\Nto help us to adjust to the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.08,1:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that we don't seem to be able to just\Ngrasp in ordinary life. So then we'll
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.60,1:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,move on from childhood\Nto the next level. What happens after
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.28,1:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,childhood?\NUh
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.48,1:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens after childhood then is\Nadolescence.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.08,1:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we can successfully\Ncome out of childhood then uh we come
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.23,1:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,out into adolescence\Nwhere again we are in a world of world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.19,1:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,events. It's either a dangerous world or\Na safe world. It's an emotional climate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.96,1:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then adolescence financial adequacy of\Nthe family and yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.88,1:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of social acceptance,\Nthe education that you receive,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.44,1:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your friends and f and comrades,\Nthe emergence of sexuality and hormones
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.04,1:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and your preparation for it. And here of\Ncourse we're profoundly
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.71,1:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in involved in herity.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.36,1:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the attitudes that we grow up with then\Nare as you can see the the result of a
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.88,1:12:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,complex interaction of biologic and\Nsocial and family cultural and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.15,1:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship. Next\Nthen the next thing that after you've
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.71,1:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,been through that battering gram of\Nwhammies
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.48,1:12:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you now become an adult. Oh my god. And\Nnow the problems really start.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.23,1:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? What am I going\Nto be in this world?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.15,1:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to be get married or be\Nsingle? Am I going to be heterosexual or
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.80,1:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,homosexual?\NAm I going to be part of a group? Am I
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.32,1:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be isolated?\NMarriage and the family become extremely
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.71,1:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,important. And again, adverse effects\Ncan happen to you and searching for
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.67,1:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,success.\NAnd we're all affected without are
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.60,1:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,really being aware of it uh of world\Nconditions. I tend to keep my eye on the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.60,1:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,news and period periodically throughout\Nthe day catch up with world events
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.56,1:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because world conditions affect your own\Nemotional attitudes and expectations
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.15,1:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without you being aware of it. You'd\Nsay, 'Well, that's all happening out
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.67,1:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Out, but out there is actually\Nwhere you live. Out there is really you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.60,1:13:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can turn the TV set around and see that\Nyou are you are the out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.96,1:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, of course, your health profoundly\Naffects you and your financial
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.48,1:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,situation.\NAging has its own profound effects on
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.71,1:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,attitudes and your politics, political,\Nyour intellectual capacity and
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.71,1:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,interests. If your interests are in the\N400s, if you're intellectually
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.48,1:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in the great books of the\Nwestern world, you will end up more
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.56,1:14:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophic and sophisticated.\NWe have the introvert versus the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.28,1:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,extrovert. And of course, we're all\Nprofoundly affected by our physical
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.92,1:14:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,appearance.\NSome people, like myself, are
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.67,1:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,good-looking.\NI have to fight off the women.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.92,1:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us have to adjust to the fact\Nthat we are not looking like Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.28,1:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Uh but does happiness depend on\Nthat? No. I've known some ugly really
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.12,1:14:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly people. They were hard to look at.\NThey were extremely happy
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.84,1:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and some be beautiful people extremely\Nmiserable. And as a psychiatrist, I saw
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.28,1:15:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,them all. Handsome young men who have a\Nnegative self-image and should be out
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.12,1:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there and successful in every area.\NLovely women who so you have to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.23,1:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,surmount. These are the things we have\Nto surmount and by our spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.84,1:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution\Nuh we transcend these things which to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.23,1:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,other people are limitations.\NSo I don't want anybody out there to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.36,1:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,have any limitations.\NCross out all limitations.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.23,1:15:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an unlimited being. You're\Nsubject only to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.80,1:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an unlimited being. You're only\Nsubject to what you hold in mind. If you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.36,1:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,think you're stupid and ugly, I got news\Nfor you. You're stupid and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.19,1:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you're lovable, then you\Nare lovable.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.96,1:16:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you're not lovable, then\Nyou're not lovable. So, we re really
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.60,1:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,become that which we hold in mind. And\Nthat's why we went through these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.76,1:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These are things that people just take\Nfor granted without thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.04,1:16:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're in psychoanalysis\Nand have to lay there and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.32,1:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and discuss all these things with your\Nanalyst.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.76,1:16:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The average person then has to surmount\Nall these obstacles to fulfillment and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.08,1:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through these obstacles in order\Nto reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.36,1:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're interested primarily in\Nreaching the levels of enlightenment and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.76,1:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore we want to successfully\Ntranscend all these stresses of ordinary
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.32,1:16:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,life. Good enough\N>> everybody for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.96,1:17:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you work like a dog to reach\Nenlightenment and then you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.15,1:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nobody to become enlightened.\NYou thought there was somebody or some
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.32,1:17:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,individual that's going to become\Nenlightened and you find out that that's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.23,1:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,fiction.\NYou've wasted your life pursuing fiction
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.67,1:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're going to become enlightened\Nand then you discover there is nobody to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.76,1:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,become enlightened. What a relief.\NNobody here has to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.56,1:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to buy into that goal of\Nlife. You say the heck with
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.28,1:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment.\NI just want to be stupid and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.48,1:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To be happy if you're stupid and ugly\Nmeans you're enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.23,1:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> All right. So, we're going to take a\Nbreak for how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.64,1:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> For about 15 minutes.\N>> We're going to take a 15minute break.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.76,1:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI want everybody to stay out of trouble
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.80,1:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for 15 minutes.\N>> Can you stay out of trouble for 15
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.12,1:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes? That's the question.
